name: Cute Ancient Egyptian Catgirls Bastet and Sekhmet Appeared??!
name_original: Cute Ancient Egyptian Catgirls Bastet and Sekhmet Appeared??!
description:
If a pair of cute catgirls appeared at your doorstep... What would you do???

Now... What if they were cute catgirl gods??!!

You don't have anything you wouldn't want them to see, right??!

A short comedy visual novel poking fun at the catgirl genre.

DISCLAIMER:

Some routes may contain content that some may find disturbing.
